burn(uint256).notice: Will expand the supply of the reserve currency.Deposit from msg.sender.

burnFor(address,uint256).notice: Will expand the supply of the reserve currency.

claimRewardFor(address).notice: Specifically allows for others to push reward.

hasClaimed(address).notice: Used to restrict reward claims per  account.

isTerminated().notice: If true, depositors may claim a refund.

mint(uint256).notice: Will expand the supply of the reserve currency.Deposit from msg.sender.

mintFor(address,uint256).notice: Will expand the supply of the reserve currency.

renounceOwnership().notice: Allows the owner to remove ownership claim without treansfer.Reverts if a proposed owner is set to other than address(0);

subjectToken().notice: This token is accepted as deposit for the case stufy.Would provide the backing for the reserve currency.
